Frederik Aust

Hi, I’m a postdoctoral researcher in the Psychological Methods group at the University of Amsterdam. I develop and test mathematical models of human cognition using Bayesian statistics and try to improve the computational reproducibility of psychological science. I also create R packages.

To find out more about me and my work,
have a look at CV the following links.
